  "detailed_description": "Beat The Moles is an arcade game where you have to hammer at the moles that hide and sometimes crawl out of their holes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game is limited in time, so you have to manage to hit a large number of moles in short periods of time to get extra time.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs the game progresses, its pace accelerates and you should make an effort not to lose.",
